-- Diamond Offshore Drilling CEO Lawrence Dickerson to retire
-- 
-- Tue Sep 24, 2013 7:33am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/24/us-diamondoffshore-ceo-idUSBRE98N0GE20130924

 

 (Reuters) - Diamond Offshore Drilling Inc ( DO.N ) said its Chief Executive Lawrence Dickerson has decided to retire, after being with the offshore oil and gas drilling contractor for 34 years. 
 Dickerson would remain chief executive until a successor is found, expected by March 31, 2014, the company said. (Reporting by Aby Jose Koilparambil; Editing by Kirti Pandey)